ng new movies-for-dummies

npm install

***** general
ng generate component __________      or ng g c ______________    - makes a component in the app file
ng g class models/_____       - puts a .ts file in a new folder "models"
ng g enum types/______ -   enum.ts file in "type" folder - helps define what data should be in the models folder
ng g service service/_______  - adds a _____.ts, and _____.spec.ts in a "service folder

create our components
ng g component admin
ng g component auth/login
ng g component auth/register
ng g component home
ng g component movie
ng g component movie/movie-details
ng g component movie/movie-add
ng g component movie/movie-edit
ng g component post
ng g component post/post-details
ng g component post/post-add
ng g component post/post-edit
ng g component bymovie
ng g component details

create a service folder. add the services to it
ng g service services/home
ng g service services/movie
ng g service service/post
ng g service services/auth

create models folder   -  ng g class folder/file
ng g class models/movie
ng g class models/user
ng g class models/post

ng generate guard auth/auth


ng add @angular/material       - look up documentation. angular 10 changed it all


